Mikkia was a planet with a variety of climates located in the galaxy's Expansion Region, and home to the Mikkian species. Mikkia was a member of the Galactic Republic for thousands of years. The destruction of the Jedi Order contributed to a high level of anti-Imperial sentiment on Mikkia.
